but no date was set gorbachev speaking briefly with reporters 
summarized the meeting by saying we will let the fruit grow ripe 
and when the fruit grows ripe we will eat it 
it was the first meeting between leaders of the two countries 
which have never established diplomatic relations since korea was 
divided between victorious us and soviet forces who liberated the 
