coming closer they probably will never be fully alike there is 
no need for that 
he implored scientists in both countries to join in determining 
how nuclear weapons could be destroyed without harming people or the 
environment 
he also advocated a system of international alliances that unites 
rather than divides the world 
the cold war is now behind us let us not wrangle over who won 
