betty whose job in a company formed by wright and mallick was 
questioned by the ethics committee said there are deeper feelings 
i think that it leaves scars i dont think theres any way to 
get away from it she said 
wright maintained that the ethics charges were falsely brought by 
his enemies and that he never knowingly violated house rules he 
