ethics allegations started flying 
i thought i could let the other guy wear brass knuckles if 
he wanted to and i could still win he said maybe thats 
hubris it turned out that it didnt work that way 
nevertheless he insists hes not bitter 
im happy im as busy as i want to be he said 
