marines coast guard national guard and the reserves joined bush on 
stage as representatives of the 1 million program participants 
the montgomery gi bill provides up to 300 a month in benefits 
for fulltime students but montgomery wants to raise the monthly 
stipend to 400 
bush a close friend of montgomerys said the gi bill ranks 
among the most practical and costefficient programs ever devised 
cheney called it crucial for recruitment and retention he said 
reserves were twice as likely to stay in the reserves in 198588 
if they were saving for college 
the size of our force may come down in the future but quality 
