tuesday with footage of gorbachevs presidential airplane touching 
down at vnukovo 2 airport it then broadcast the speech the soviet 
leader delivered to cheering students in california on monday 
in moscow the mood of rebellion was spreading to the very center 
of soviet power the congress of peoples deputies of the russian 
federation met in the kremlin and elected yeltsin as its president 
may 29 the day gorbachev departed moscow 
gorbachev had opposed yeltsins election saying his plan to 
shift economic and political decisionmaking from the central 
government to the russian republic could lead to the disintegration 
of th soviet union 
