his creditors has denied that financial and legal troubles were 
connected with the flight 
on monday a nash county grand jury in raleigh nc returned a 
455count indictment charging root with securities fraud and other 
charges also indicted were sonrise management services telemedia 
inc and three other men identified as coowners of the two 
businesses 
root handled radio license applications for investors of sonrise 
management 
the indictments allege the companies violated securities laws by 
not registering securities failing to register sales agents 
engaging in false and deceptive sales practices and conspiring to 
violate securities laws 
