document indicating its license application had been reinstated and 
defrauded another north carolina client by settling a claim against 
a competitor for onefifth the authorized amount 
root pleaded guilty to giving a false document to a new york 
client seeking a site on long island for a radio station and 
falsely telling another client he would get an fcc application 
reinstated when he had sought the dismissal 
