don ensminger 
ensminger has told the freedom fighters that 
bridgestonefirestone wishes to continue operating its plantation 
and keep jobs available to the 8500 liberian employees and 
their more than 85000 dependents they have told him the fight was 
not with him or the plantation employees and they do not intend any 
destruction hoskins said 
