he said the bodies had bullet wounds the hands were tied and 
many were blindfolded all the bodies were wrapped in tightly bound 
sacks he said 
digging so far has been limited to a single trench but hevia 
said authorities planned to open two more possible gravesites 
after taking power in a violent coup on sept 11 1973 the 
