trumps brief statement on monday 
at this point these are things that are between the trump 
organization and other people and were not at liberty to talk about 
that klores said 
investors have been unsettled by reports that the banks were 
trying to prevent trump from making upcoming payments to junk 
bondholders such a move would devastate the value of the risky 
securities which are attractive to investors because they pay a 
much higher interest rate than other bonds 
trumps lenders are believed to be concerned that his holdings 
including the casinos are not producing enough cash to meet 
interest payments 
