problems he did announce in late april that he was considering 
putting some of his assets on the block including the northeast 
air shuttle he bought from eastern airlines for 365 million last 
year but claimed he wanted to raise cash to buy new properties 
trumps other assets include the plaza hotel trump tower 
skyscraper and several apartment buildings in manhattan 
