of 365 million in may a monthly record for an atlantic city 
casino the win averaged 118 million a day industry analysts have 
estimated it needs to make between 1 million and 13 million a day 
to break even 
the journal reported that the big banks also were concerned that 
if trump does sell assets he might not be able to get the kind of 
prices that he claims they are worth 
the journal story followed a string of negative reports about how 
well trumps empire is doing forbes magazine recently sliced its 
estimate of the developers net worth to 500 million from more than 
15 billion 
trump has maintained he was having no liquidity problems 
