survival it said 
in mexico as in other third world countries poverty and 
population growth compete for environmental protection 
the government has declared reserves protected specific species 
and passed environmental laws private organizations are becoming 
more openly active 
in mexico city a program taking cars and trucks out of 
circulation one day a week has reduced overall air contamination 10 
to 15 percent the government says other sources say less with 
ozone the main contaminant not affected 
