tomkins plc has agreed to acquire philips 
industries inc in a stock conversion deal worth about 550 million 
both companies said today 
under the agreement in principle each outstanding share of 
philips common stock would be converted into 1850 per share in 
cash philips would be merged with a tomkins subsidiary 
daytonbased philips makes components for residential commercial 
and industrial buildings manufactured housing recreational 
vehicles and the transportation industry 
tomkins based in london is an industrial management company 
that owns and operates manufacturing and distribution businesses 
primarily in the united states and united kingdom 
