it will take longer now because the courts will have to approve 
any financial restructuring 
the companys total debt stood at 384 million at the end of 
march the debt is the legacy of a 270 million leveraged buyout led 
by currey three years ago that took the company private a few 
months later the group paid 80 million for dallasbased trailways 
lines inc 
